<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../002/439002.xml">
Curitiba</link></city>
, HDI of 0.856 (information of 1996). The region, along with the state of São Paulo, is characterized also for the strong immigrant presence (Italians, Germans, Portuguese, Spanish, Poles, Japanese, Arabs, Ukrainians and Lithuanians), that gave the region their typical aspects (architecture, culinary, agriculture of subsistence, etc).</entry>
